# PROJECT_CONTEXT_INPUTS.yaml (template)
#
# Purpose: Stable, testable inputs for generating PROJECT_CONTEXT.md without a guided interview.
# - Keep values factual and explicit.
# - Use `None` or `Not applicable` when that is the truth.
# - Prefer short concrete statements over generic planning boilerplate.
#
# Notes:
# - Only mechanically derivable fields should be defaulted automatically by tooling.
# - `key_modules_or_areas` may be empty when no concise module list is needed.
# - `integrations` may be empty when the project has no meaningful external contracts to track.
#
